  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Asciidoctor</title>

    <para>
      Asciidoctor is a fast, open source text processor and publishing
      toolchain for converting AsciiDoc content to HTML5, DocBook, PDF, and
      other formats.
    </para>

    &lfs121_checked;

